room_title: Escape room "Sulley’s Sinking Ship" by Escape Zone Oxford in Oxford (AL)
room_description: Following a brutal storm, Captain Sulley finds himself and ship battered and in trouble. As you and your team begin rescue efforts, the desperate Captain struggles to confide that a long-rumored treasure actually exists and manages to mumble a few words pointing you in the direction of where to begin the search. You must work fast though – the ship is taking on water from the storm damage and is sinking.
